data.description: Offered $7000 below recently appraised value AND sellers offering a $5000 Use as You Choose Allowance with an acceptable offer! Check out this gem in North Jacksonville, Onslow County!  This 3-bedroom, 2-bath, 2-car garage patio home is what you've been waiting for.  Picture yourself on the charming covered front porch, enjoying lazy afternoons in your rocking chair. All three bedrooms conveniently located on one side of the house for easy living. Step inside, and you'll be greeted by a spacious living room with a vaulted ceiling, creating an open and airy feel. The kitchen boasts stainless appliances, a handy pantry, and yes, the fridge is included - PLUS the laundry room is right off the garage and kitchen for your multi-tasking awesomeness. Both bathrooms have been updated, and there's a newer water heater, too. You'll find ceiling fans in all the bedrooms for added comfort. The owner's suite has not one, but TWO closets and a stylish trey ceiling with a fan. Imagine entertaining or just relaxing on your huge covered back patio, overlooking your fenced backyard. And if you like working on projects or need extra storage, the 2-car garage comes with a pass-thru door to the backyard. Concerned about the unknowns? Don't be! The seller has already had a pre-listing home inspection and pest inspection, and they've taken care of many of the items on the report for your peace of mind. Plus, there's a low HOA fee of just $235 a year, which includes access to the community pool. And when you're ready for a change of scenery, you're just a short drive from some of North Carolina's beautiful beaches. Whether you're a first-time buyer or a savvy investor, this home checks all the boxes. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity.... call a Realtor in coastal NC today for more info!
